{"name":"Standing Orders","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"hindrance","data":{"description":"<p>While your adventurer may have his own goals, he ultimately serves another power and is expected to follow orders when they are issued. An adventurer with this Hindrance may be a knight or spy, a contracted mercenary, a guild mage, or a Trinity crusader, for example.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"major":false},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Plnd93ciQNNZl1P8"}
