{"name":"Hades Wants You (Major)","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"hindrance","data":{"description":"<p>Your character believes he has drawn the unwanted attention of the invisible lord of the underworld. Such attention can be deadly. All Soak rolls and rolls to avoid death are at -2 (see Incapacitation in the Savage Worlds rule book). The character cannot take the Hard to Kill or Harder to Kill Edges.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"major":true},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","effects":[],"_id":"Jz7bUfGGNG4WoW27"}
