{"name":"Sense of Duty (Minor)","permission":{"default":0,"89eyOdrISceMvDfi":3},"type":"hindrance","data":{"description":"<p>This Hindrance is similar to loyal except it is linked to a polis rather than a group of people or friends. Note that the sense of duty is to a polis and its people, not necessarily towards any given leader. Patriots who believed they acted in the best interests of their home and people have initiated many rebellions.</p>","notes":"","additionalStats":{},"major":false},"flags":{},"img":"systems/swade/assets/icons/hindrance.svg","effects":[],"_id":"CrfnSGa31AjdXSs0"}
